plot: A woman in an open marriage suddenly gets strong belly pain. Taub would like an open marriage. Wilson's new relationship with his ex is shaky.

House and the team take on the case of a woman Julia, who is in an open marriage and becomes ill during a date with her on-the-side boyfriend. As perplexing as the case is, Julia's happy and healthy, yet polygamous relationship is equally baffling to the team. Meanwhile, House tests Wilson's relationship with Sam.—Fox Publicity
